{"id": 821, "genre": 1001, "title": "你都给什么匪夷所思的东西取过名字？", "description": "过分热爱生活的一个你。（题图：Janne Livonen）", "record_count": 2933, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 0, "image": "img/paper/paper_show/20160607194624e950cUjhK6AFxEmq.jpeg", "page_style": 0, "category": 2, "column": 2, "type": "paper", "date": "2016-02-22T11:08:45Z", "options": [{"id": 52484, "content": "床上的女朋友", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 74156}, {"id": 52485, "content": "叫学校，因为喜欢人叫薛骁", "image": null, "praise_count": 5, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 314556}, {"id": 53765, "content": "猫咪后院里的所有猫。影大，机械君，老袜……", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 490365}, {"id": 52486, "content": "随手的一件物品，一个玩物，虚构的剧情中的人物", "image": null, "praise_count": 5, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 485609}, {"id": 52487, "content": "就在刚才，我硬是想不起小多的原名叫益力多??", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 485617}, {"id": 52488, "content": "模拟人生里面的人物一定要起一个与众不同的名字！！！", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 354380}, {"id": 52490, "content": "我家的扫地机器人?️  罗伯特", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 338898}, {"id": 52491, "content": "会给小区里经常喂的那些的流浪猫流浪狗起名字，大喵 ，小喵、五饼 、瓦力 、癫仔、大花、白鬼…", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 410927}, {"id": 54283, "content": "中二病，给自己虚幻的学生", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 447066}, {"id": 52492, "content": "左脚袜子", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 485647}, {"id": 52493, "content": "给日记起了个名字叫小E", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 205329}, {"id": 53262, "content": "去大便?叫“噢笃茄”（粤语发音拉泡屎的意思，但字面发音是韩语）", "image": "img/option/option/20160606004839yPm8izWA4aEu71nX.jpg", "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 487820}, {"id": 52495, "content": "我高中同桌有支笔，我特别喜欢用那支笔，还给它起名叫“一支笔”，我每次想用，都跟同桌讲，把“一支笔”那给我用用。后来高考结束的那天，同桌把“一支笔”送给了我", "image": null, "praise_count": 5, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 485641}, {"id": 53520, "content": "每一个U盘 都有着自己专属的名字 还带性别划分的=￣ω￣=", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 251751}, {"id": 52497, "content": "蓝牙叫一头老母猪。然后好多人要和我配对?", "image": null, "praise_count": 6, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 484468}, {"id": 54545, "content": "给每件衣服起一个名字，小黄，小黑，小花之类的", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 82933}, {"id": 52501, "content": "我用奖学金买的土豪金手机，叫小哆，哆啦A梦的哆?", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 466131}, {"id": 60694, "content": " 我家的娃娃，长的很恶心的娃娃", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 528763}, {"id": 52510, "content": "橡皮擦，就是那种，一套的彩色的方块的橡皮擦，我给它们取过名字?", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 469429}, {"id": 54304, "content": "自己。。。", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 494216}, {"id": 55840, "content": "初中上学路上有买活鸡的，味道不好，和同学起名叫“臭霸”", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 502358}, {"id": 55331, "content": "不知道名字的花|･ω･｀)", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 490571}, {"id": 52772, "content": "给qq分组取好听的名字，并且认真分类", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 381568}, {"id": 52517, "content": "长得一模一样但大小不同的公仔…比如流氓兔、泰迪熊什么的…", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 481225}, {"id": 52519, "content": "我曾经用名字来区分我的人格", "image": null, "praise_count": 8, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 485782}, {"id": 52526, "content": "车子叫小白，笔记本电脑叫小红，机械键盘叫小七…", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 465761}, {"id": 53040, "content": "不同味道的風", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 487317}, {"id": 52530, "content": "孩子的娃娃", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 481199}, {"id": 52531, "content": "Iphone的设备名称", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 485885}, {"id": 53555, "content": "电脑的CDEF盘。分别叫做:人家不要做C盘，小C又在撒娇了，老D不要理她，无聊的主人。", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 330854}, {"id": 52532, "content": "我的各种wifi分别取名为kfc、mcdonald、chinamobile、chinaunicom，从来没人蹭网，这叫假作真时真亦假，此地无银三百两。", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 405835}, {"id": 52533, "content": "我的wifi名: 密码:我是一个大傻逼", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 485890}, {"id": 52278, "content": "给我小侄女大侄儿起啥文艺名字\r\n", "image": null, "praise_count": 8, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 188225}, {"id": 53558, "content": "右手", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 419435}, {"id": 52281, "content": "手机里的应用合集，一定要想个好听的名字", "image": null, "praise_count": 329, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 141966}, {"id": 52538, "content": "家里的电饭煲叫阿圆，因为它长得小小个，圆溜溜的。", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 485959}, {"id": 52283, "content": "小时候给各种工具，扳手钳子螺丝刀玻璃刀……", "image": null, "praise_count": 17, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 464636}, {"id": 52539, "content": "叫我的手机“阿?”“小??”“?”，每次找不到手机了就会听到、我的?呢！我的小??呢！", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 416547}, {"id": 52795, "content": "给自己的信起各种匪夷所思的名字。", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 486601}, {"id": 52284, "content": "我的汽车叫小滴 买的第一套房叫H1（house one)", "image": null, "praise_count": 21, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 484375}, {"id": 52540, "content": "还有谁会给10010和10086存通讯录", "image": "img/option/option/20160606161701RGsMJhwqgVcv65kZ.jpg", "praise_count": 20, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 336579}, {"id": 52285, "content": "匪夷所思的设备名字/账户名/闹钟/WiFi", "image": null, "praise_count": 72, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 21033}, {"id": 52286, "content": "我妈从小把我不吃的东西都取了个好听的名字来骗我吃。", "image": null, "praise_count": 103, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 161957}, {"id": 54334, "content": "我的电子设备，连电脑后各种改", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 495183}, {"id": 52287, "content": "几乎所有东西?", "image": null, "praise_count": 9, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 227136}, {"id": 52543, "content": "车叫二旺，扫地机器人叫三旺。它们的姐姐是一只猫，叫喜旺……", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 337192}, {"id": 52288, "content": "把桌面上所有东西塞进一个文件夹，然后取名“这是桌面上唯一的文件夹”", "image": null, "praise_count": 101, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 484384}, {"id": 53312, "content": "媳妇基本上一天都会有几个名字", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 487975}, {"id": 52289, "content": "我给手机上的文件夹起名。出行类app文件夹叫独步行天下。学习类app叫升技能打怪兽。。。。等等", "image": null, "praise_count": 7, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 5363}, {"id": 53313, "content": "新建一个微信群，起名“这是一个用来扯淡的群”╮(─▽─)╭", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 279250}]}